# Startup notes:
# 1. Start MongoDB first on 127.0.0.1:27017.
# 2. If the service is not available, start it manually with:
#    mongod --dbpath .mongo-data --port 27017 --bind_ip 127.0.0.1
# 3. Then run start.bat --no-pause from the repo root.
# 4. Verify /api/health returns mongoConnected=true before testing batch details.

